SANITIZED SHOWCASE — NOT THE PRODUCTION SYSTEM
==============================================

This repository is a clean-room re-implementation of the *architecture* of a
multi-marketplace resale automation system built for a client (an anonymous,
US-based resale business). It exists only to demonstrate the engineering.

By design, this repo does NOT contain:
  • The production code — that lives in a separate, private repository.
  • Any real marketplace integration — those adapters are proprietary client
    work and stay private.
  • Any credentials, cookies, browser sessions, endpoints, SKUs, or client data.

Every marketplace adapter here is a fake (`FakeMarketplaceClient`) that performs
no network I/O and holds no secrets. All inventory data is synthetic.
